1. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - This is the most likely category as the paper is about breaking an image encryption scheme and reporting security defects. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - Information theory is closely related to cryptography and encryption, and the paper may involve some information theoretic analysis. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - Chaotic maps are often used in control systems, and the paper may involve some analysis of the system dynamics. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper is specifically about an image encryption scheme, which falls under the category of multimedia. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - Image encryption is also related to computer vision and pattern recognition, and the paper may involve some analysis of the image processing techniques used in the scheme.
